episodes.title: 'Knee deep into the cult of Donald Trump': Defense asks Cohen if he was obsessed with Trump
episodes.description:
The defense asked Michael Cohen if he was "obsessed" with former President Trump as the cross-examination continues. Former FBI General Counsel Andrew Weissman, former Assistant Manhattan District Attorney Catherine Christian and criminal defense attorney Duncan Levin join Katy Tur and Chris Jansing to analyze.
